The paper focuses on Visual Question Answering (VQA), which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also introduces a new dataset and a new model for VQA, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper involves analyzing and comparing different models, which could be related to information retrieval (cs.IR).
